svt_axi_port_monitor_callback Class Reference

Inheritance diagram for class svt_axi_port_monitor_callback:

List of all members.

Detailed Description

Port monitor callback class contains the callback methods called by the port monitor component. The coverage callback classes are extended from port monitor callback class.
